<span class="ws0">-</span></span></div><div class="t m0 x2b h1b y164 ff57 fs7 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws4a2">ers who were willing to go the extra miles for people they had ne<span class="_ _0"></span><span class="ws0">v<span class="_ _0"></span>er met. </span></div><div class="t m0 x2b h28 y209 ff55 fs1f fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">J<span class="_ _0"></span><span class="wsfc">uan Chauquian is a lay worker living in Zaleta Manzana, Chile<span class="ws0">.</span></span></div><div class="t m0 x2d h24 y108 ff60 fs1c fc0 sc0 ls0 ws5d">Produced by the General Conference Office of Mission Awareness </div><div class="t m0 x2d h24 y109 ff60 fs1c fc0 sc0 ls0 ws26d">E m a i l : g o m i s s i o n @ c o m p u s e rv e. c o m</div><div class="t m0 x25 h2 y10a ff55 fs0 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">63</div></div><div class="pi" data-data='{"ctm":[1.000000,0.000000,0.000000,1.000000,0.000000,0.000000]}'></div></div>
